Senator FEINSTEIN. Thank you. Thank you, Mr. Chairman. 
The  CHAIRMAN.  And  I  think  this  just  demonstrates  to  all  of  us 
that  the  forthcoming  debate  will  be  a  very  serious,  mature,  and 
productive one. 

Thank you very much. 
