McGinn  for  bringing  in  the  security  issue.  I  hope  the  Senate  and 
the  Committee  listened  to  you,  because  the  security  issue  is  the 
turning  point  on  this,  as  far  as  I’m  concerned.  And  I  think  if  we 
listen to you, we will get a bill that will make some sense. 

