Mr. FRIEDMAN. A plug-in hybrid—— 
Senator CARPER. Plug-in hybrid on a—the Ford Taurus? 
Mr. FRIEDMAN. On a Ford Taurus, exactly. 
Senator  CARPER.  I’m  just  wondering  why  Ford  didn’t  hire  you. 
